            <H2>ABOUT AURORA</H2>

            <p>Welcome to the colorful world of Aurora Brickwell, where imagination meets the art of Lego.
            It all began in the quiet corner of her grandfather's attic, where a dusty, old chest brimmed with
            Lego pieces ignited Aurora's love affair with building. As a child, Aurora was enchanted by the
            stories her grandfather told, of places and people far away, and she spent countless hours crafting
            these tales into tangible Lego landscapes. With each brick clicked into place, Aurora discovered
            that she could build not just structures, but gateways to any world she wished to explore.
            </p>

        </div>
